        "content": "<p>Is it possible to \"temporarily\" <code>rw</code> something while passing it as a term?</p>\n<p>E.g. instead of</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">foo</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bar</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I wish I could do</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bar</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">foo</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>or something like that. Is that possible?</p>\n<p>I'd want that <code>rw</code> to be scoped to that call only.</p>",
        "id": 504809536,
        "sender_full_name": "Dan Abramov",
        "timestamp": 1741691815
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Maybe <code>bar (by rwa [foo] at h)</code></p>",
        "id": 504810228,
        "sender_full_name": "Ruben Van de Velde",
        "timestamp": 1741692008
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Or <code>bar (foo \\t h)</code></p>",
        "id": 504810320,
        "sender_full_name": "Ruben Van de Velde",
        "timestamp": 1741692036
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>More generally: <code>by</code> lets you go from term mode to tactic mode in any subterm of an expression. Conversely, <code>exact</code> or <code>refine</code> lets you go from tactic mode to term mode.</p>",
        "id": 504848970,
        "sender_full_name": "Floris van Doorn",
        "timestamp": 1741701406
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Exactly and <code>\\t</code> could be seen as a term mode version of <code>rw</code> so basically exactly what you want.</p>",
        "id": 504909138,
        "sender_full_name": "Robin Arnez",
        "timestamp": 1741714210
